Pressure
 costs 1 Anger
 take an action which results in 1 Leverage gain against target.

Fight
 rqr 2 Leverage
 target pc. incur a cumulative -1 penalty to their Force moves.

Suspect
 target pc. incur a cumulative -1 penalty to their Fool moves.

Cower
 costs 1 Fear
 Force moves against you
 pass the turn to the gm.

Flee
 costs 2 Fear
 escape unscathed. leave the encounter. pass the turn to the pcs.

Argue
 rqr 2 Leverage?
 target pc. incur a cumulative -1 penalty to their Reason moves.

Flirt
 target pc who just flirted with you. incur a cumulative -1 penalty to their Flirt moves. you have Leverage against that pc equal to the total penalty. 
